Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.56,0:00:15.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,[新机动战记-钢弹W]\NJust Wild Beat Communication
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.76,0:00:19.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受到雨水拍打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.23,0:00:22.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,决不褪色的炽热思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.77,0:00:27.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,传遍你的全身 TONIGHT!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.88,0:00:41.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱着你被淋湿的肩膀 想温暖你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.09,0:00:48.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,颤抖的指尖 彷徨地在找什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.89,0:00:54.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想留住你的视线
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.17,0:01:02.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相信把悲伤变为力量的爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.61,0:01:10.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受到雨水拍打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.28,0:01:13.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,决不褪色的炽热思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.92,0:01:17.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,传遍你的全身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.62,0:01:19.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,TONIGHT!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.18,0:01:47.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第二十九话\N[战场的英雄]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.55,0:01:51.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,罗姆斐拉财团的支配制度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.56,0:01:52.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,遍及全世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.99,0:01:55.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,它所到之处都发生纠纷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.73,0:01:58.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,本国也主张和平主义
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.33,0:02:00.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,制止胡乱的抵抗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.53,0:02:04.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,归入他的支配下\N的确能得到和平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.24,0:02:07.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但那根本不是真正的和平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.04,0:02:08.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是压制
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.97,0:02:12.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,压制又会产生新的纠纷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.38,0:02:16.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们的行动有成绩吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.15,0:02:17.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在历史里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.55,0:02:19.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,世上有许多国家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.85,0:02:22.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,许多民族和许多思想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.25,0:02:26.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,发生若干纠纷\N或许是无可避免的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.79,0:02:29.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,自由是赐予所有人的权力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.80,0:02:30.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.53,0:02:34.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,完全自由不被认同也是必须的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.10,0:02:38.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和平共处须要的关怀别人的心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.74,0:02:41.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,绝对不是战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.14,0:02:44.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,从过去学习\N创造正确的新未来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.74,0:02:46.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是我们的工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.65,0:02:48.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我认为反抗罗姆斐拉财团
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.91,0:02:51.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有本国是做不到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.02,0:02:54.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没错，山克王国这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.65,0:02:57.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是已故匹斯克拉福特国王提倡的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.26,0:02:59.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,完全和平义生根的国家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.59,0:03:02.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是我们强大的支柱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.09,0:03:04.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只是遵从我父王的教诲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.33,0:03:09.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我十分明白\N我这种人的言行很失礼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.50,0:03:11.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，为了令更多的国家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.64,0:03:15.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,更多的人能得到真正的和平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.21,0:03:18.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我请求各位协助我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.11,0:03:20.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们一起努力吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.19,0:03:34.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,顺利结束了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.09,0:03:34.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.93,0:03:38.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们并非在监视各位的行动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.56,0:03:42.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看来比原定快了很多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.20,0:03:44.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们意见一致
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.80,0:03:47.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以才不必花太多时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.64,0:03:50.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么，被讨厌的人也告辞了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.34,0:03:52.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是眼中钉吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.24,0:03:56.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们并非讨厌罗姆斐拉财团
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.35,0:03:59.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们只是希望她快点纠正错误
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.32,0:04:02.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在许多生命消失之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.70,0:04:13.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,伯爵，宇宙服有两件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.30,0:04:16.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,降下的看来果然只有那两人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.10,0:04:19.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道，看来也不用戒备了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.74,0:04:20.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.57,0:04:21.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.61,0:04:27.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宇宙卫星和罗姆斐拉财团结盟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.61,0:04:29.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们的任务已经结束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.88,0:04:32.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有命令要处死钢弹的驾驶员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.58,0:04:34.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,处死他们很简单
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.75,0:04:37.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,本国也归入\N罗姆斐拉财团的支配下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.72,0:04:40.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但我想搁置他们的处决
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.78,0:05:05.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡特尔，你讨厌动物吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.72,0:05:07.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我很喜欢啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.09,0:05:08.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么，和它们玩吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.95,0:05:11.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,它们看来比较喜欢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.76,0:05:16.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,动物本能地知道谁是仁慈的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.23,0:05:19.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,战争须要那种仁慈吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.06,0:05:20.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不须要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.33,0:05:22.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,战斗不须要啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.10,0:05:26.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是\N战斗以外的时间就须要吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.57,0:05:30.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在不是战斗时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.59,0:05:43.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不客气了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.12,0:05:44.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很是对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.42,0:05:47.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,本应有命令要处死我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.59,0:05:48.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幸好总部有联络来说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.03,0:05:52.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们亲自前来接收钢弹驾驶员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.73,0:05:55.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不用亲手杀死你们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.03,0:05:56.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我实在很高兴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.94,0:06:01.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，到时我同样要交出你们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.64,0:06:03.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们不能再麻烦你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.91,0:06:06.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请你照指示做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.08,0:06:09.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们打算束手就擒吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.05,0:06:11.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,时候未到还不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.58,0:06:14.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但我们没打算白白送死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.22,0:06:16.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们好坚强啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.12,0:06:17.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我对本国参加罗姆斐拉财团的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.69,0:06:21.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,支配政策抱有疑问
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.19,0:06:23.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但为了避免无益的战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.13,0:06:25.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们只好选择这条路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.30,0:06:28.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是保护许多生命正确决定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.90,0:06:32.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们的宇宙也做了相同的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.37,0:06:34.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们对罗姆斐拉财团来说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.57,0:06:36.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是个障碍\N但只有这样..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.37,0:06:38.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,才有存在意义的钢弹驾驶员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.91,0:06:41.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,来取自己性命的人是敌人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.61,0:06:44.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不想死的就只有战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.12,0:06:46.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在我们能做的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.42,0:06:50.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定要做的只有那样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.89,0:06:52.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果不想死的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.60,0:06:59.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,运输机听好，马上投降
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.66,0:07:01.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们奉命击落你们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.53,0:07:03.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,重覆，马上投降
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.90,0:07:06.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,北纬50度，很冷呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.54,0:07:09.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，不可以乖乖交给OZ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.72,0:07:51.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那里吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.82,0:07:58.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快点走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.70,0:08:08.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莎莉‧普奥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.93,0:08:10.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要感谢我们帮你取暖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.64,0:08:13.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新OZ是个仁慈的组织
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.81,0:08:16.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是确认运输机里有什么之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.14,0:08:19.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是重要的客人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.54,0:08:21.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然我听说\N只要钢弹的驾驶员行动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.31,0:08:24.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和他们有关的叛乱份子就会出现
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.68,0:08:29.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但想不到能得到钢弹啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.65,0:08:33.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,钢弹的驾驶员果然回到地球了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.19,0:08:35.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我无论如何要把那东西\N交给他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.96,0:08:37.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.06,0:08:39.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,参加罗姆斐拉财团的国家\N急速增加
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.60,0:08:42.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今后不会轻易成功呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.34,0:08:50.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是钢弹的就不会有金属反应
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.38,0:08:52.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但有运输机的金属反应
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.34,0:08:54.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剔除那反应   是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.25,0:09:00.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么事?   敌袭吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.62,0:09:07.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谁?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.66,0:09:09.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想知道真相
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.29,0:09:11.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沉在海底的是真的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.96,0:09:14.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我或许会说谎骗你救我出去呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.70,0:09:17.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为了对抗罗姆斐拉财团
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.07,0:09:18.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想要钢弹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.70,0:09:20.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们和相同的敌人战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.54,0:09:25.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快决定是否进行交易
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.71,0:09:27.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,连决定的时间也没有呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.11,0:09:28.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么走啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.60,0:09:49.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然是真的吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.57,0:09:51.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以，敌人的集结也很快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.00,0:09:54.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是OZ称为01的机体啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.84,0:09:57.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,另外，你说想钢弹帮助你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.58,0:09:59.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的国家在哪里?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.51,0:10:01.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在不能说，我只能告诉你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.61,0:10:03.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是个因为反抗罗姆斐拉财团
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.38,0:10:06.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而不知何时会被攻击的国家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.99,0:10:09.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今后的时代需要的人物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.09,0:10:11.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,正在统治那国家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.36,0:10:13.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个人能为这世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.19,0:10:15.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,带来真正的和平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.76,0:10:17.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你认为只靠钢弹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.26,0:10:20.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就能打赢罗姆斐拉财团?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.64,0:10:31.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那些驾驶员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.91,0:10:36.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定能粉碎罗姆斐拉的野心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.05,0:10:38.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们都认识钢弹的驾驶员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.55,0:10:41.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那令我们经常鲁莽行事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.85,0:10:44.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我认为倚靠他们会有问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.32,0:10:47.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但现在，我想要他们的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.13,0:10:49.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谁也不想有战争
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.59,0:10:52.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但有能力战斗的人就应该战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.70,0:10:54.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是那样想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.87,0:10:57.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然说什么正义是大言不惭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.24,0:11:00.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但那些孩子配得起那字眼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.21,0:11:03.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其实那或许是可悲的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.24,0:11:06.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为他们迫作为时代的英雄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.28,0:11:08.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但我想追随他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.51,0:11:09.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我认为那样会令我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.51,0:11:12.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用走上错误的路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.70,0:11:32.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,消灭钢弹的作战\N在两处地方进行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.80,0:11:35.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一处是我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.24,0:11:38.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,另一处\N是希洛你留下的钢弹吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.61,0:11:40.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被称为01的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.65,0:11:42.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大概是了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.25,0:11:45.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛，你认识山克王国吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.42,0:11:47.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在罗姆斐拉财团的机密资料里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.89,0:11:50.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她被记录为问题国家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.62,0:11:53.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,山克…王国
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.56,0:11:54.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然有巧妙地掩饰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.96,0:11:57.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但他们非常严密的监视着01
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.86,0:12:00.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还有它的驾驶员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.06,0:12:01.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想去呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.63,0:12:04.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想去帮助他们呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.04,0:12:14.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,乖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.58,0:12:17.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,监视我们的只有这两只狗啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.02,0:12:20.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是叫我们走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.32,0:12:23.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这个国家不希望有战争
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.25,0:12:25.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们是战斗的火种呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.36,0:12:27.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这里的司令官也有弱点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.79,0:12:29.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就是仁慈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.86,0:12:31.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,走吧，卡特尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.01,0:12:49.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有机影正接近这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.71,0:12:51.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,坦辛特伯爵有联络来吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.62,0:12:52.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.72,0:12:54.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,马上确认吧   是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.65,0:12:55.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.35,0:12:57.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们朝罗姆斐拉的部队去了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.26,0:12:58.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们为何不逃走?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.89,0:13:00.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是那部队的紧急来电
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.69,0:13:02.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,叫我们联络接近中的飞机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.03,0:13:05.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,坦辛特柏爵，这是他们留下的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.30,0:13:07.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,钢弹驾驶员给我的吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.50,0:13:08.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,伯爵，说什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.90,0:13:11.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,[希望你马上报告我们逃亡了]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.74,0:13:15.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,[我们不可以再为你们添麻烦]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.57,0:13:16.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.67,0:13:17.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多谢你，伯爵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.98,0:13:19.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其实我们逃走就行吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.64,0:13:21.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但我们要战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.88,0:13:23.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,逃去哪里也一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.61,0:13:27.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们只能战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.99,0:13:29.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们真可怜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.10,0:13:45.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敌袭!敌袭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.61,0:13:52.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不客气了!去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.64,0:13:53.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.54,0:13:56.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.95,0:13:58.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,发现敌人!鱼雷发射
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.86,0:14:10.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么事?敌人吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.28,0:14:32.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然鲁莽，但只有这样做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.38,0:14:34.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道很鲁莽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.82,0:14:38.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想要他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.29,0:14:40.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为了山克王国
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.11,0:15:02.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,举手!反抗是无用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.55,0:15:04.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,麻烦你们也联络其他战舰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.25,0:15:08.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们不想再增加伤亡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.39,0:15:12.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,照他说话做比较好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.79,0:15:15.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,若是我，我马上就会攻击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.43,0:15:18.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我其实希望你不要动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.23,0:15:21.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，那种事不可能呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.64,0:15:32.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛，今后去哪里好呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.28,0:15:36.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我没有想去的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.45,0:15:39.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,地球有很多仁慈的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.75,0:15:41.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但如果我们去他们那里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.59,0:15:45.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们就会令他们有麻烦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.69,0:15:48.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们已经无处可去呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.06,0:15:51.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡特尔，因为你想忘记战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.93,0:15:53.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要地球是战场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.00,0:15:55.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就要战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.40,0:15:58.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且，你也只好战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.87,0:16:02.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们是钢弹的驾驶员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.54,0:16:05.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只容许活在战场上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.84,0:16:08.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在战斗中活下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.05,0:16:12.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就是我们的生活吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.56,0:16:20.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是莎莉，这边成功镇压了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.96,0:16:21.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你那边如何?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.96,0:16:25.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们正在久别重逢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.06,0:16:27.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你用它帮助你的国家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.40,0:16:29.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起，多谢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.83,0:16:31.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我叫路克蕾琪亚‧诺茵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.90,0:16:33.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我效力的国家叫…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.34,0:16:35.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,诺茵，不用了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.57,0:16:37.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使不知道你的国家的名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.81,0:16:40.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也会相信你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.58,0:16:42.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要能协助反抗罗姆斐拉的国家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.61,0:16:45.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我已经觉得很光荣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.62,0:16:46.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莎莉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.92,0:16:49.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我去搜索其他钢弹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.22,0:16:51.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,若得到有关情报\N你再来支援我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.02,0:16:53.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.29,0:16:55.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有两三个驾驶员就信心培增呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.76,0:16:57.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一定会去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.60,0:17:00.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为了令你也相信我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.13,0:17:04.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我向神和本国的名字发誓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.36,0:17:37.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,监视和平国家的人正要回去吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.07,0:17:44.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特地赶来的我真像个傻瓜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.08,0:17:47.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我还以为利用这机会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.38,0:17:50.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,进攻山克王国
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.62,0:17:53.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，靠MD一定不足够
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.99,0:17:55.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为那种木偶没理由敌得过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.69,0:17:58.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,保护公主殿下的骑士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.82,0:18:00.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.52,0:18:03.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今日来的转校生没问题吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.06,0:18:05.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么?柏根
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.23,0:18:07.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我听闻\N那和罗姆斐拉财团中心人物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.60,0:18:10.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,迪尔麦优侯爵有血缘关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.27,0:18:12.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然你会责备我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.54,0:18:14.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但我认为是讨厌山克王国
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.57,0:18:20.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和平主义的某财团的策略
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.54,0:18:21.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,罗姆斐拉财团说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.08,0:18:23.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们只是相学习山克王国
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.31,0:18:25.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,建设和平国家的教育方针
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.32,0:18:29.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以派留学生转校来这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.55,0:18:31.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不用担心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.82,0:18:36.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不能相信财团的一切言行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.39,0:18:38.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怀疑别人不会有用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.76,0:18:42.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且，我们无愧于心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.57,0:18:44.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我认为也是一个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.57,0:18:46.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能令他们明白那一点的好机会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.08,0:18:53.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是本学园的理事长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.14,0:18:55.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜‧匹斯克拉福特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.31,0:18:57.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,欢迎光临山克王国
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.72,0:18:59.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不知道山克王国的公主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.88,0:19:03.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也兼任学园的理事长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.32,0:19:04.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,重新自我介绍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.79,0:19:06.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,桃乐丝‧卡塔罗尼亚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.52,0:19:08.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我好尊敬你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.09,0:19:10.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一个人仍然什么也做不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.03,0:19:13.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我正在一起学习
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.83,0:19:16.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我父王提倡的完全和平主义
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.80,0:19:18.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如你所知
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.27,0:19:21.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是从罗姆斐拉财团来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.54,0:19:23.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,财团现在于这个战乱之世
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.84,0:19:25.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拥有大量武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.28,0:19:30.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我对山克王国的方针\N非常有兴趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.21,0:19:32.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果那些人攻来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.32,0:19:34.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想知道你会怎样做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.75,0:19:39.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这种美丽的风景\N会在一瞬间消失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.12,0:19:43.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想到那种事，连心也会被迷住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.33,0:19:45.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谁也不想眼白白看着这国家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.96,0:19:48.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被那种野蛮的笨蛋催毁呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.43,0:19:50.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那时候，你会怎样做呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.74,0:19:54.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我认为这个世上没有笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.01,0:19:57.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对话就能互相了解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.11,0:20:00.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我相信那会给予所有人和平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.01,0:20:02.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.38,0:20:04.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也是笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.38,0:20:07.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我喜欢战争，好喜欢啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.32,0:20:11.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我这种人在这个国家是障碍呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.19,0:20:13.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不，山克王国的首要目标
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.52,0:20:17.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是成为能这样子讨论的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.33,0:20:21.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今后也时常讨论吧\N桃乐丝小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.73,0:20:26.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你叫我桃乐丝就行\N莉莉娜殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.07,0:20:28.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请你也叫我莉莉娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.24,0:20:29.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.94,0:20:32.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜殿下是时代的英雄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.01,0:20:36.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为莉莉娜殿下你是我的偶像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.95,0:20:41.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,桃乐丝‧卡塔乐尼亚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.55,0:20:43.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和莉莉娜殿下相同年纪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.69,0:20:45.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,至于她是独立行事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.42,0:20:47.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还是被罗姆斐拉支配
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.83,0:20:51.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我暂时还未清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.26,0:20:53.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，不能太意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.06,0:20:54.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别放松监视
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.57,0:20:57.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也准备了这种东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.87,0:21:00.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但桃乐丝小姐看来很难应付
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.60,0:21:02.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么意思?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.77,0:21:06.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,桃乐丝小姐看来非常喜欢战争
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.91,0:21:10.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在莉莉娜殿下\N想否定战斗的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.82,0:21:12.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我相信她的存在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.15,0:21:15.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,会令莉莉娜殿下很疲倦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.15,0:21:17.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜殿下的想法非常好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.66,0:21:20.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是明知不适合这时代的行动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.69,0:21:21.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,保护那样的莉莉娜殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.89,0:21:24.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是我们的使命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.56,0:21:27.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使拿起武器也好呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.30,0:21:28.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.40,0:21:30.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不可以让莉莉娜殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.73,0:21:33.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,像这国家\N被暗杀的国王一样遇害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.74,0:21:36.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们正在面对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.17,0:21:39.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,绝对不可以重覆的历史
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.72,0:21:55.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使使用任何卑鄙手段
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.69,0:21:57.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也要保护莉莉娜殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.90,0:22:00.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要成为这国家的影子活下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:09.01,0:22:11.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快点爆发战争吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:13.58,0:22:15.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,待续
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:24.76,0:22:31.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,心血来潮的找人出来\N只因为天气好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:32.76,0:22:38.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,让我一直等不到人\N你以为你是谁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:39.76,0:22:43.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道你是跑过来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:43.76,0:22:46.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但那也是应该的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:47.26,0:22:53.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Just Love ! 那个惹人厌的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:54.76,0:23:01.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捉弄人  是因为心理有爱意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:02.26,0:23:09.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Just Love !  老是让人挂念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:10.76,0:23:17.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起\N我不该说出强人所难的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:17.76,0:23:19.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,‧‧‧Just Love‧‧‧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:33.29,0:23:35.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,罗姆斐拉财团的势力不断扩大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:35.53,0:23:37.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在世界各地气势如虹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:37.19,0:23:39.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛成为反抗的特列斯派
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:39.90,0:23:40.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,某部队的雇庸兵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:40.97,0:23:43.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,随意地参加了战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:43.10,0:23:44.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡特尔对战斗会解决一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:44.67,0:23:46.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱有疑问
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:46.14,0:23:48.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这时的卡特尔得知了抵抗财团
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:48.34,0:23:52.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,主张完全和平主义的国家的存在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:52.94,0:23:55.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新机动战记-钢弹W，第三十话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:55.55,0:23:58.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和莉莉娜的重逢

